Description:
STYLISH FAMILY ENTERTAINER
This beautiful red brick family home has a steel frame and Colorbond roof.
It features 4 bedrooms, master with generous walk in robe and a mirrored door built in robe plus a luxurious ensuite with separate toilet. The 3 remaining bedrooms have mirrored door built in robes, all robes are 2 metres high and have double hanging and shelving.
There are two living areas, formal lounge with feature fireplace, all rooms have plantation shutters, double glazed awning windows and ornate light fittings with gorgeous ceiling roses.
The stylish kitchen includes 40mm stone benchtops, a great walk in pantry, 900mm electric oven and 900mm gas cooktop, fridge space with water point, in tap water purifier and double built in bin system.
All cabinetry has two pack finish with decorative handles, the kitchen has ample drawers and storage options. The laundry has an abundance of storage area, laundry clothes hamper, a built in ironing station and is strategically located close to the kitchen.
Ducted evaporative cooling and ducted gas heating, the family/dining area also has a split system for year round comfort an Alarm system, Ceiling height 8'6".
Solar hot water with instantaneous boost, 5kw solar system to keep electricity bills low.
Double garage with internal house access
Generous alfresco area with extra large double doors and TV point
Additional outdoor area with open brick fireplace perfect for entertaining in the cooler months
6 x 8 metre shed ideal for the caravan and boat, with extra high double front roller door and a single roller door and personal access door to the back yard. There is an additional 6 x 9 metre shed with two single roller doors and personal access door, this shed includes extensive storage shelving, built in work bench and sink, a shower and toilet. It really is the ultimate man cave. It has a large concrete area running the length of the shed, both sheds have concrete floor and power.
There are undercover and exposed clothes lines with ample concrete paths around the entire property. Automatic sprinkler system to all gardens and lawns including raised vegetable patches and herb garden. Low maintenance yard featuring garden lights and cottage plants, fully fenced with new Colourbond fences.
All of the hard work is done simply move in and start enjoying life with the beautiful Murray River walking distance from this quiet court location.
Call for an inspection this property is sure to impress!

Description:
Executive Living ~ Beautifully Designed
Superbly presented three bedroom, split level home, cleverly positioned on an elevated block in an excellent part of Cobram, only a short walk to the Murray River. This stylish residence features an open plan living area split over two levels with a tiled entry, carpeted lounge room and a study nook on the lower level. The upper level features a stunning designer kitchen with quality stainless steel appliances, generous meals area and living space with timber floor. Three generous bedrooms with built in robes, main with walk in robe and ensuite. Ducted heating and cooling, and ducted vacuum system.
